A '''water supply''' is a primary industry that only appears in the [[en/Manual/Climates]]. It produces [[en/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Water]] which should be delivered to a [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Water Tower]], but does not accept any cargo. A water supply can only be built in desert areas.

